ollapsed":false,"created_time":1546011149,"updated_time":1546011149,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会不会被清华北大录取我不知道 我只知道他的闹钟过会就要响了 马上又要去学校补作业了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561884485,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"081d2c5cb31ef93dd358d2bb18d5427d","url_token":"wu-jing-tian-ze-78-41","name":"毋净殄泽","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/081d2c5cb31ef93dd358d2bb18d5427d","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561884485","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546010826,"updated_time":1546010826,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e等你把证明过程发出来的时候，就应该做好心理准备，因为将有成千上万的人要挑你的毛病，如果被推翻，那么你能承受的了吗？但是，如果后来发现你的证明是完美的，那么恐怕就不只是清华北大那么简单了，一个如此之大的跨世纪数学难题被证明出来，整个数学界都将为之轰动，不排除有数学大家将来想收你为徒的想法\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561808466,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561808466","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546003142,"updated_time":1546003393,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个话题火爆程度远超想象啊。我有点担心题主会被喷，受到心理创伤……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e钱钟书当年数学15分，进了清华，如果你确实如你所说，在数学研究中表现出了极高的天赋，有机会被发掘，别说清北数学系了，Stanford、MIT、巴黎高师怕是争着抢着要你，哪怕你英语烂到只会abc。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你若真的有能力，又何恐会被埋没呢？这还是一个尊重知识的世界。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用行动说明一切吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561756948,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ff425a15b8533fd7341e44608b78bc31","url_token":"xue-ding-e-de-miao-98","name":"工农联盟","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ff425a15b8533fd7341e44608b78bc31","user_type":"people","headline":"河北高四狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561756948","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545996903,"updated_time":1545996903,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你在问这个这个问题之前，最好先看看自己会不会这个题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e已知函数f(x)=ex(ex﹣a)﹣a²x．\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）讨f(x)论的单调性；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（2）若f(x)≥0，求a的取值范围．\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e建议你考虑考虑自己能不能上个本科，不要整天想哥德巴赫猜想这些东西。你这个问题和如果我征服了世界的话，可不可以管理一个县一样\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561741832,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"279f2b9e07a03fe34c625547656b257a","url_token":"dgk-81","name":"DGK","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/279f2b9e07a03fe34c625547656b257a","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561741832","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995172,"updated_time":1545995172,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的这么年轻就做到了，那么题主应该考虑的问题是“我能否被称作人类自文明建设以来最了不起的数学天才？在我的余生（18岁左右的余生有点长讲道理…）我能为数学界带来多大的革新？”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561731802,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f176fe30ae66c639d0cfe68f3c066cb1","url_token":"lu-ling-jun-43","name":"陆凌君","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3cd6c279016a4737695c55827a0a1d66_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3cd6c279016a4737695c55827a0a1d66_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f176fe30ae66c639d0cfe68f3c066cb1","user_type":"people","headline":"这个人所有的回答都是编的","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561731802","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545994008,"updated_time":1545994008,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我的天啊，这真的不是概率微小的问题啊。概率无限趋近0跟概率严格等于0是不一样的啊。就好比说，我就算再怎么秋名山车神也不可能把AE86开上月球吧？因为这已经不是车技能解决的问题。哥德巴赫猜想也已经解释过是不能用初等数学知识来解决了，这和题主的数学天赋高不高根本没有任何关系。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e做不到就是做不到，让题主承认这个事实很难吗？数学从来就不是什么有梦想谁都了不起的学科，前沿工作者都是在黑暗中摸索着寻找方向，有的人穷极一生都在黑暗中不断碰壁，为的是什么？不就是希望后来者能少走点弯路吗？前人都探出来这是一座高山了，题主还拿个两米高的小梯子就想爬上去。这除了浪费大好青春还有什么意义？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e正是因为题主还年轻才需要尽早让他清醒过来。题主现在正站在人生重要的十字路口，骂他的人或许只是想装个逼，而安慰他的人才是真的想毁了他。。。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561696558,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3279e3b3ed5a5566c8570e942e27714a","url_token":"xu-hui-74-79","name":"瓶子","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3279e3b3ed5a5566c8570e942e27714a","user_type":"people","headline":"岩土工程","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561696558","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545990202,"updated_time":1545990202,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个问题就如同是在问：当我成为了世界首富，我还去街头要饭被人认出来会不会给我100块钱。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561688050,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a8085e0fe936d976271c32f1ca0fe5d7","url_token":"clairad","name":"Clairad","avatar_url":"ht